        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>
            <icon-wc name="package" size="sm"></icon-wc>
            Zero Dependencies
          </h3>
          <p>No frameworks, no build tools, no npm required. One CSS file, one optional JS file.</p>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>
            <icon-wc name="palette" size="sm"></icon-wc>
            OKLCH Theming
          </h3>
          <p>30+ themes across color, personality, and extreme categories. Apply with one attribute on any element.</p>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>
            <icon-wc name="layout-grid" size="sm"></icon-wc>
            Layout Attributes
          </h3>
          <p>Stack, Grid, Cluster, Sidebar, Dashboard — add <code>data-layout</code> to any semantic element. No wrapper divs.</p>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>
            <icon-wc name="accessibility" size="sm"></icon-wc>
            Accessible
          </h3>
          <p>ARIA patterns built-in. Keyboard navigation with Arrow, Home, End, Escape. Accessibility themes including high contrast.</p>
        </article>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Theme Lab -->
  <section class="theme-section">
    <h2 data-blur-reveal>One Attribute, 30+ Themes</h2>
    <p class="theme-lead">Pick a theme. Watch everything transform.</p>

    <figure class="theme-lab">
      <figcaption>
        <label>Theme
          <select id="theme-lab-select">
            <option value="default">Default</option>
            <option value="swiss">Swiss</option>
            <option value="organic">Organic</option>
            <option value="brutalist">Brutalist</option>
            <option value="kawaii">Kawaii</option>
            <option value="terminal">Terminal (Dark)</option>
            <option value="8bit">8‑bit (Dark)</option>
          </select>
        </label>
      </figcaption>
      <iframe id="theme-lab-frame"
              src="/docs/tools/theme-lab/surfaces/home-preview.html"
              title="Theme preview"
              loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </figure>

    <footer data-layout="cluster" data-layout-justify="center">
      <a href="/docs/themes/" class="button secondary">Browse All Themes</a>
    </footer>
  </section>

  <script type="module">
    const select = document.querySelector('#theme-lab-select');
    const frame = document.querySelector('#theme-lab-frame');
    if (select && frame) {
      const base = '/docs/tools/theme-lab/surfaces/home-preview.html';

      select.addEventListener('change', () => {
        const params = new URLSearchParams();
        if (select.value !== 'default') params.set('theme', select.value);
        frame.src = `${base}?${params}`;
      });

      window.addEventListener('message', (e) => {
        if (e.data?.type === 'surface-height' && e.source === frame.contentWindow) {
          frame.style.height = e.data.height + 'px';
        }
      });
    }
